# Month/Year + Money Inputs

## Month/Year

- Do not use native `input type="month"`.
- Use `MonthYearPicker` (`src/components/inputs/MonthYearPicker.tsx`).

Rules:
- Month UI uses `T1..T12`.
- Year list max is 5 years.
- Component must be responsive (no modal overflow).

## VND amount

- Use `VndAmountInput` (`src/components/inputs/VndAmountInput.tsx`) for amount fields.
- Store numeric value (integer VND), but display formatted `1.000.000`.

